title: Unnatural Omega
description:
They say misery loves company, but I don’t think having a dark, controlling alpha steal you away is what they meant.
Especially after everything you know about yourself has been changed.When a horrible accident yanks me away from my life of mourning, I wake up in a bright, unbearable torture chamber.Then the devil finds me and whisks me away to hell.He’ll keep me, even if he has to bind me to him against my will.Unnatural Omega is the second scorching-hot, action-packed, Omegaverse book in a series of seven, perfect for those who love reading steamy dark paranormal romance.
author: V.T. Bonds
